Package com.microblink.entities.recognizers.blinkid.mrtd

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    MrzFilter
    Filter for MRTDs (Machine Readable Travel Documents) that is used to determine which documents will be processed.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MrtdCombinedRecognizer
    Recognizer for combined reading of face from front side of documents and MRZ from back side of Machine Readable Travel Document.
    MrtdCombinedRecognizer.Result  
    MrtdDocumentType
    Supported MRTD document types
    MrtdRecognizer
    Recognizer that can recognize Machine Readable Zone (MRZ) of the Machine Readable Travel Document (MRTD)
    MrtdRecognizer.Result  
    MrzResult
    Represents data extracted from MRZ (Machine Readable Zone) of Machine Readable Travel Document (MRTD).
